gh-open-pr - GitHub Pull Request Creator

USAGE:
    gh-open-pr [base-branch] [head-branch]

DESCRIPTION:
    Create a GitHub pull request using console context information
    for title and description.

ARGUMENTS:
    base-branch
        Base branch for PR (optional)

    head-branch
        Head branch for PR (optional)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-github-gh-notification METHOD
        Notification method after PR creation

EXAMPLES:
    gh-open-pr
    gh-open-pr main feature-branch
    gh-open-pr develop my-feature
